Currently the player supports monoscopic (equirectangular) videos with 360-degree view, the original would look like this:
With the possibility to render them as a 360 panorama or in &ldquo;cardboard mode&rdquo; if the cardboard icon is clicked. To enable the VR feature showCardBoardView has to be set to true.
&lt;video id='vr-video' crossorigin=&quot;anonymous&quot;&gt; &lt;source src='monoscopicvideo.mp4' title='1080p' type=&quot;video/mp4&quot; /&gt; &lt;/video&gt; &lt;script&gt; fluidPlayer( 'vr-video', { layoutControls: { showCardBoardView: true, showCardBoardJoystick: true } } ); &lt;/script&gt;
